sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant REST as MLServer REST<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant GRPC as MLServer gRPC<br/>8081/TCP gRPC (insecure)
    participant DP as DataPlane Handler
    participant Batcher as Adaptive Batcher<br/>(asyncio queue)
    participant Cache as Response Cache<br/>(in-memory FIFO)
    participant Codecs as Codec System
    participant Model as MLModel Runtime<br/>(sklearn/xgboost/lightgbm/onnx)
    participant Parallel as Parallel Worker Pool<br/>(multiprocessing.Queue IPC)
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>/mnt/models (PVC/S3)

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: REST Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (kube-rbac-proxy)
    Gateway->>REST: HTTP 8080/TCP<br/>No encryption (cluster-internal)
    REST->>DP: In-process routing
    DP->>Cache: Check cache (request hash)
    alt Cache Hit
        Cache-->>DP: Cached response
    else Cache Miss
        DP->>Codecs: Decode request inputs<br/>(numpy/pandas/string)
        Codecs->>Model: MLModel.predict()
        Model-->>Codecs: Prediction result
        Codecs-->>DP: Encoded response
        DP->>Cache: Store in cache
    end
    DP-->>REST: InferenceResponse
    REST-->>Gateway: HTTP response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC ModelInfer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>GRPC: gRPC 8081/TCP<br/>No encryption (cluster-internal)
    GRPC->>DP: In-process routing
    DP->>Codecs: Decode tensor inputs
    Codecs->>Model: MLModel.predict()
    Model-->>Codecs: Prediction result
    Codecs-->>DP: Encoded response
    DP-->>GRPC: ModelInferResponse
    GRPC-->>Gateway: gRPC response
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC/HTTP2 response<br/>TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: Adaptive Batching
    par Multiple concurrent requests
        Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer (req 1)
        Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer (req 2)
        Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{name}/infer (req 3)
    end
    REST->>DP: 3 concurrent requests
    DP->>Batcher: Enqueue all 3 requests
    Batcher->>Batcher: _merge_requests()<br/>Combine into single batch
    Batcher->>Model: MLModel.predict(batched)
    Model-->>Batcher: Batched prediction
    Batcher->>Batcher: split_response()<br/>Separate individual results
    Batcher-->>DP: Individual responses (x3)
    DP-->>REST: Responses
    REST-->>Client: Individual HTTP responses

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 4: Parallel Worker Inference
    REST->>DP: Inference request
    DP->>Parallel: ParallelModel proxy
    Parallel->>Parallel: Dispatcher (round-robin)<br/>Select worker process
    Parallel->>Model: multiprocessing.Queue IPC<br/>to subprocess worker
    Model->>Model: MLModel.predict()<br/>(in isolated subprocess)
    Model-->>Parallel: Response via IPC queue
    Parallel-->>DP: Inference result
    DP-->>REST: Response

    Note over Client,Storage: Model Loading (Startup)
    Storage->>Model: Load model artifacts<br/>from /mnt/models
    Model->>Model: Parse model-settings.json<br/>Initialize runtime
